high_descs: Walk to the sink on the other side of the table.
Grab the fork from the sink.
Turn around and walk to the  table.
Place the fork in the glass on the table.
Grab the glass from the table.
Turn around and walk to the counter to the right of the sink.
Place the glass on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a glass with a fork in it on the counter to the right of the sink.

high_descs: Turn to the right, and then the left to walk around the island. Locate the sink on the right.
Pick up the fork from the sink
Hold the fork and turn around to the island.
Place the fork in the glass to the right of the plate.
Pick up the glass and fork from the island.
Carry the glass and turn around to the sink.
Place the glass and fork on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move a glass and fork to the counter.

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen sink in front of you.
Grab the fork out of the sink.
Go to the kitchen table behind you.
Place the fork inside the wine glass.
Grab the glass with the fork in it.
Walk back to the kitchen sink.
Place the glass with the fork in it on the edge of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a fork in a glass to set up near the sink.
